<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990823.0072 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-23 09:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6277 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-R-BESTSELLERS-PAPER-S     08-23 1098
</HEADER>
<BODY>
