<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-TURKEY-GREECE-REVIEW-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A NATURAL DISASTER HELPS DRAW TWO ENEMIES CLOSER 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(lh) 
 By STEPHEN KINZER    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
