<SLUG> BC-R-AIR-SAFETY-REVIEW-655&AMP;ADD-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A BACK-DOOR VIEW OF AIRLINE SAFETY 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(lb) 
 By MATTHEW L. WALD    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Right after ``What does it cost?'' the question
