<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-23 10:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6317 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-R-DEATHROW-REVIEW-3TA     08-23 3439
