a list of a host of new reviews. And there's a look at the 10 best
games scheduled for release next year. The new games include
Freelancer, Throne of Darkness, Alone in the Dark 4 and Planet of
the Apes. (Haddad, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED.
