<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-23 13:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6506 &Cx1f; sci-z
r a BC-MUSICAL-MUSCLES-NYTSF     08-23 1224
