<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-23 14:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6521 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-TAXCUT-VOTERS-BOS &LR;      08-23 1117
