<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Flowers in the Dustbin: The Rise of Rock and Roll, 1947-1977''
by James Miller (Simon &AMP; Schuster, $26.). A guided tour of the
glory days of the music that parents were never meant to like. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
