</P>
<P>
   HKN-NHL-MONEY (Boston) _ Clearly, as the weeks and months go by,
the NHL becomes increasingly polarized. There are the haves, the
have-nots, and in the Bruins' case, the will-nots. By Kevin Paul
Dupont. (2 takes)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-08-23-99 1500EDT &QL; 
