connects consumers with Web sites that match their individual
interests, today announced that Sergio Zyman, one of the world's
foremost marketers, will lead strategic efforts to build eTour's
in-house marketing organization and spearhead the company's
branding campaign. (Katz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
