   HDEPOT-MUSEUM _ A new corporate museum at Home Depot's
headquarters in metro Atlanta officially opens tomorrow,just in
time for the company's 20th anniversary celebration downtown. About
4,000 managers are slated to attend the four-day meeting, which is
expected to be equal parts shop talk, pep rally and party. (Bond,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
