Bradlees Inc. and Ames Department Stores, among others, have used
bankruptcy as a safe harbor where they can fix their problems. By
Chris Reidy. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   FED-RATES (Undated) _ Federal Reserve Board is expected to raise
rates by another quarter-point. The increase may not be the last
this year, analysts say. By Kimberly Blanton. 800 words.
