<P>
   TEN-USPRO (Brookline, Mass.) _ By Rupen Fofaria.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN (Brookline, Mass) _ By Bud Collins.
</P>
<P>
   RUN-WORLDS (Seville, Spain) _ The matchup of impressario El
Guerrouj and upstart Ngeny is one of the most eagerly awaited of
the 1999 meet. By Barbara Huebner.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-PATRIOTS (Smithfield, R.I.) -- If the Patriots roster were
set today, the midpoint of the preseason, there would be few
changes from last year. By Nick Cafardo.
</P>
<P>
   BBA-TWINS (Minneapolis) _ By Larry Whiteside.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
