<HEADLINE>
3,000 `CELEBRATE' PERROT'S LIFE AT HOUSTON MEMORIAL SERVICE 

</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  By W.H. STICKNEY JR. 
c.1999 Houston Chronicle 
 
