<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-23 21:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7020 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a BC-BRET-STORM-HNS &LR;      08-23 1483
