<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-23 21:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7080 &Cx1f; taf-z
u d BC-SOUP-FAD-COOLS-NYT &LR;      08-23 1148
