<HEADLINE>
JONES ONLY THIRD-BEST LONG JUMPER
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Fixing headline) 
By KIRBY LEE  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   SEVILLE, Spain _ Marion Jones already has proven she is the
